title: Gardeners World 2016 Episode 19 [Sr_Soil]
description:
Episode 19
Gardeners' World, 2016

Now that rambling roses have finished flowering, Monty turns his attention to pruning and tying in new growth for a good display next year.

On the 20th anniversary of the death of Geoff Hamilton, Adam Frost returns to the famous Gardeners' World location, Barnsdale, to pay tribute and to revisit some of his own early gardening memories.

And we travel to Abergavenny to visit the garden of a sweet pea enthusiast, to get her top tips for growing the best blooms
